4. HOW TO PLAY\
-----------------------------------------\
- Use **WASD**  to move Pac-Man.\
- Collect all pellets to clear the level.\
- Avoid ghosts unless they are frightened.\
- Collect power pellets to enter "Frighten Mode," allowing you to eat ghosts for bonus points.\
\
